g.text: asks to display a list of properties
gives the options to filter [type of business (buying or renting),
type of property (house, apartment or land) and the number of rooms]
[Filters by type of business, type of property and number of rooms]
selects all the options to filter (type of business, type of property
selects only the type of business
selects only the type of property
selects only the number of rooms
[Filters by type of business and type of property]
selects the type of business and the type of property
[Filters by type of business and number of rooms]
selects the type of business and the number of rooms
[Filters by type of property and number of rooms]
selects the type of property and the number of rooms
asks to order the list of properties
gives the options to order (price, city or state)
displays the list of properties with the sorting method selected
